    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p><em>from the mailing list... from krazynio@gmail.com</em></p>

<p>In Zend_Controller_Action, the signature of method run() is:
    final public function run(Zend_Controller_Dispatcher_Interface $dispatcher,
                              Zend_Controller_Dispatcher_Token    $action)</p>

<p>Bug is in this function on line 111:
        $methodName = $dispatcher-&gt;formatActionName($action-&gt;getActionName());</p>

<p>The method "formatActionName()" hasn't been defined in
Zend_Controller_Dispatcher_Interface. It means that even if you have a
dispatcher implements Zend_Controller_Dispatcher_Interface, it can't
be used in Zend_Controller_Action.</p>

